title: [Mairiseth Telearat, Courtyard]
description: Resaeun-latticed partitions of verdant foliage create leafy backdrops for a trio of floral-engulfed gowns, the colorful trains curtaining across the cobblestones.  A flute-tiered champagne fountain rises across the center of the expansive courtyard, the glinting of jade-colored glass reflecting across some pale marble benches scattered nearby.
